	   <tr><td colspan=2>mathmaticly you just said that it does and doesnt reduce ratio, well the truth is... it increases swings over time which also means LOWER DELAY, it is just a diffrent calculation than most people think. it is delay/1 + % of haste so lets take the delay of the BaBs and these gloves (lets say a 10% haste) 39 divided by 1.10 and your new delay is... 36.1<br><br>all im saying is you are right that it increases swings over time, but that means you are reducing delay! <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Jun&nbsp;&nbsp;2 07:47:05 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Midgie Hobbitson<br>Halfling Warrior of the 50th Battle<br>Morell Thulle </td></tr>
