	   <tr><td colspan=2> alright guys and gals, you are getting to complicated. look at it like this. if you normally swing your weapon 40 times a minute that is the average 100% you have. if you were to add a extra 10% to that it would mean you swing 44 times. thats 100%plus 10% (110% or 1.1) times 40 equals 44. yes i realize this item is 11% haste but for my simplized purposes that extra 1% just added more trouble than it was worth. the math would have been 111% or 1.11 times 40 equaling 44.4 hits per minute, which as you know would have equalled 44 anyway. /shrug<br><br>Kathrin Spiritbear<br>Shaman of the Tribunal<br>Knight of the White Rose<br>Tallon Zek<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
